Enum Class BinderType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<BinderType>
BinderType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<BinderType>, Constable
public enum BinderType extends Enum<BinderType>
Enumerates the different types of binders available in the Trading Card Inventory System. Each binder type represents a specific category with different characteristics and restrictions.

The available binder types are:

  • BASIC - A standard binder with no special restrictions
  • PAUPER - A binder specifically for common and uncommon cards
  • RARES - A binder designed for rare and legendary cards
  • LUXURY - A premium binder for high-value cards
  • COLLECTOR - A special binder for complete collections
